Report No 1 received from US Consumer Relations, Date 10-DEC-2014, Reference No: R061721970.
Suspect Drug: Mucinex Unspecified (Unspecified Mucinex).
Dosing: Unknown.
Case reference number US-RB-071220-14 is a spontaneous case report sent by a consumer or other non health 
professional which refers to a patient of unknown sex aged 7 years.
The reporter (Mother) stated that her 7 year old child took Mucinex Unspecified for an unknown indication on an 
unspecified date. The patient developed a nose bleed.
The reaction was deemed serious by the company because it was classed as medically significant due to epistaxis.
